<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Poem for my Valentine</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Feb 14, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Some people tell me <br></br>
that I look through <br></br>
rose colored glasses, <br></br>
because life can’t <br></br>
be that good.
</p>

 <p>
All I know is that <br></br>
if my glass is only <br></br>
half full it’s <br></br>
because I have <br></br>
drunk deeply <br></br>
from the <br></br>
joy, <br></br>
wonder, <br></br>
and <br></br>
love <br></br>
that is you.
</p>



